292
00:41:51.908 --> 00:41:56.036
But you did open it, so. . .

293
00:41:58.665 --> 00:42:00.457
Mathilda. . .

294
00:42:00.583 --> 00:42:04.795
If you don't help me,
I'll die tonight. I can feel it.

295
00:42:04.921 --> 00:42:07.589
But I don't want to die tonight.

296
00:42:08.717 --> 00:42:11.426
Mathilda, you're just a little girl,

297
00:42:11.552 --> 00:42:15.347
