It's not professional. There is rules.

304
00:43:22.873 --> 00:43:26.584
- OK.
- And stop saying "OK" all the time! OK?

305
00:43:27.753 --> 00:43:29.421
OK.

306
00:43:29.547 --> 00:43:30.963
Good.

307
00:43:43.977 --> 00:43:45.395
Hi!

308
00:43:46.897 --> 00:43:50.483
You expect to use that
in this hotel?

309
00:43:50.609 --> 00:43:53.778
Mister, I have to use it,

310
00:43:53.904 --> 00:44:00.159
