318
00:44:32.860 --> 00:44:34.193
Fourth floor.

319
00:44:34.319 --> 00:44:35.862
Thanks, mister!

320
00:44:35.988 --> 00:44:39.991
You're lucky to have a little girl
that's interested in things.

321
00:44:41.577 --> 00:44:44.871
