and the second finishes him off.

614
01:17:21.026 --> 01:17:22.777
Never in the face.

615
01:17:22.903 --> 01:17:25.780
If they can't recognize the client,
you don't get paid,

616
01:17:25.906 --> 01:17:29.534
cause you could take out anybody
and say you did the job.

617
01:17:29.660 --> 01:17:32.203
- Got it?
- Got it. Never in the face.

618
01:17:32.329 --> 01:17:36.916
- OK. Now you can put the tools away.
- What the fuck is going on?

619
01:17:37.042 --> 01:17:38.375
