646
01:19:57.265 --> 01:19:58.724
Beat ya!

647
01:21:02.622 --> 01:21:04.581
What are you doing?

648
01:21:04.707 --> 01:21:06.750
Can't afford to catch cold.

649
01:21:54.173 --> 01:21:56.632
- There's no doorbell?
- So knock on the door.

650
01:22:01.555 --> 01:22:02.889
Yes?

651
01:22:03.015 --> 01:22:07.310
Hi, I'm looking for
Mr Rubens' apartment,

652
01:22:07.436 --> 01:22:10.730
